   ``Square Foot Gardening,'' by Mel Bartholomew (Rodale Press)
   ``The Apartment Farmer,'' Duane Newcomb (J.P. Tarcher, Inc.)
   ``Rooftop Gardening,'' Kathleen Cronin Tinkel (Chilton Book Co.)
   ``The Terrace Gardener's Handbook,'' Linda Yang (Doubleday &
Co.).
